Package: pass-extension-tail
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, pass (>= 1.7.0), gnupg2 | gnupg, bash ( >= 4.0.0)
Description: password-store extension to avoid printing the password
 An extension for the password store that allows users to display and edit
 password meta data without displaying the password itself to bystanders.
